    "Task Arithmetic.",
    "Task Arithmetic (Ilharco et al., 2023) frames model merging as vector addition and subtraction in weight space, treating fine-tuning updates as task vectors.",
    "Given a base model W 0 and its fine-tuned variant W i, the corresponding task vector is defined as",
    "These task vectors encode learned task-specific knowledge and can be algebraically combined to transfer, compose, or remove capabilities across models.",
    "A merged model W merged can thus be expressed as"
  ]
